    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs(tmp) * (wp.cos(v0 + 0.59) / (v1 + 0.78 / tmp + 0.41)))
    v1 = ((v1 - (v0 + 0.55 * v2 + 0.85)) - wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.31)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(tmp) / wp.sin(tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
